OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and widely sunny day
OL,6,Ftoday across the region, with perhaps
OL,7,Fsome cloud bubbling up later in the
OL,8,Fday. Another very warm if not hot day
OL,9,Ffor the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine and warm evening to
OL,12,Fcome, with it remaining dry overnight.
OL,13,FSome thicker cloud however will spread
OL,14,Fin from the east, especially in the
OL,15,Fnorth.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAny morning cloud will tend
OL,18,Fto burn away by lunchtime, leading to
OL,19,Fa sunny afternoon. Feeling a little
OL,20,Ffresher but still warm for the time of
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
