OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry and settled,
OL,7,Falthough a few showers may develop
OL,8,Ffrom time to time, especially later
OL,9,FThursday. Very warm initially but
OL,10,Fgradually turning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
